mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin

Class GeoWaveGTDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.geotools.data.AbstractDataStore
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin.GeoWaveGTDataStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransactionNotification, org.geotools.data.DataAccess<org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureType,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>, org.geotools.data.DataStore

    public class GeoWaveGTDataStore
extends org.geotools.data.AbstractDataStore
implements org.geotools.data.DataStore, TransactionNotification
    This is the main entry point for exposing GeoWave as a DataStore to GeoTools. GeoTools uses Java SPI (see META-INF/services/org.geotools.data.DataStoreFactorySpi) to inject this datastore.
